data.value:
The MuseArt Virtual application and MuseArt Virtual Game designed by Mert Aga in 2022. MuseArt is a virtual museum that is going from past to future. There are 3 categories in the museum, in the historycal side the Archeology and in the future side NFT's. Last, the Portrait category connects the years together. The are different types of portraits that they are similar to NFT's but with a history behind.
All exhibitions are shown detailed in the MuseArt Virtual Game. If you click Explore from the side menu you can explore the museum with the virtual reality experience. The game designed with Unity. In the virtual museum game there are 5 rooms, Portraits, NFT's, Archeology, Documentary and the middle room that it has mixed exhibits. Documentary film is about The City of Athens in Ancient Greece. Video film is copyrighted to History Hub YTTV youtube channel.
In the Exhibitins menu, you can see all exhibitions which are available for sale. Yes! You can buy a copy of each exhibit to yourself, to your friends, to your family or for everyone you love. Each exhibit can be bought only one time at once, included NFTs. After the buying proccess, the copy of exhibit will be delivered to your email within 2hrs. So, becareful when you enter your email in the Checkout Form.
If you want to Communicate with us for whatever reason you want, you can go to "Communicate" section from the side menu and send an email to us.
